  • public class ScoringModel
extends org.apache.solr.ltr.model.AdapterModel
    An org.apache.solr.ltr.model.LTRScoringModel that computes scores using a MultiLayerNetwork or ComputationGraph model.

    Example configuration (snippet): 

    {
  "class" : "org.deeplearning4j.nn.modelexport.solr.ltr.model.ScoringModel",
  "name" : "myModel",
  "features" : [
    { "name" : "documentRecency", ... },
    { "name" : "isBook", ... },
    { "name" : "originalScore", ... }
  ],
  "params" : {
    "serializedModelFileName" : "mySerializedModel"
  }
}
